263
00:15:27,426 --> 00:15:29,136
This is the Turning Point bar.

264
00:15:30,596 --> 00:15:32,056
All of those who come here,

265
00:15:33,057 --> 00:15:35,559
get the chance to change their fate.
[chuckles]

266
00:15:35,643 --> 00:15:36,727
[smirking]

267
00:15:37,227 --> 00:15:40,731
