00:16:59,226 --> 00:17:00,894
[bird chirping]

287
00:17:02,438 --> 00:17:03,439
[sighs deeply]

288
00:17:04,148 --> 00:17:05,274
Wake him up.

289
00:17:08,694 --> 00:17:11,155
-Brother, wake up.
-[murmurs]

290
00:17:11,822 --> 00:17:13,407
Wake up.

291
00:17:13,490 --> 00:17:15,200
Son, wake up.

292
00:17:15,701 --> 00:17:18,412
