311
00:18:19,098 --> 00:18:20,516
Keep it. Wear it as a cape.

312
00:18:20,599 --> 00:18:21,850
Is it possible?

313
00:18:23,101 --> 00:18:24,895
We're always here for you.

314
00:18:25,938 --> 00:18:28,649
Just don't mind me.
I can forget about Victoria.

315
00:18:28,732 --> 00:18:30,901
This pillow? Where should I put this?

316
00:18:30,984 --> 00:18:33,529
