477
00:28:18,947 --> 00:28:20,365
[cracking]

478
00:28:21,825 --> 00:28:23,910
-I will kill Humberto!
-I will kill Humberto!

479
00:28:23,993 --> 00:28:26,204
-I will kill Humberto!
-I will kill Humberto!

